OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThickening
OL,6,Fcloud this evening with showery rain
OL,7,Farriving from the northwest, although
OL,8,Fmany places remaining dry. Largely dry
OL,9,Fand cloudy overnight with occasional
OL,10,Fclear spells. A very mild night to
OL,11,Fcome.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA few brighter intervals are
OL,14,Fpossible, but for many it will be a
OL,15,Fcloudy day with occasional light rain
OL,16,Fpossible, mainly in the afternoon.
OL,17,FTurning blustery but remaining mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
