OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOften
OL,6,Fdry on Friday but windier with
OL,7,Fisolated showers. Largely fine on
OL,8,FSaturday with lighter winds and sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Brisk winds on Sunday with
OL,10,Fsome rain possible. Remaining mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
